miting.', 'Synergism', 'Oprelvekin, Elapegademase, Histamine, Pegademase, Glatiramer', 'Entrectinib, Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, Larotrectinib, Bosutinib, Vemurafenib, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/13048/', '[1] "Product Information. Zydelig (idelalisib)." Gilead Sciences, Foster City, CA.', 1767369485);
