aundice.', 'Synergism', 'Oprelvekin, Sipuleucel-T, Elapegademase, Interferon beta-1b, Peginterferon beta-1a, Interferon beta-1a, Sargramostim, Histamine, Pegademase, Pegfilgrastim, Filgrastim, Glatiramer', 'Oprelvekin, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2b, Glatiramer', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/13065/', '[1] "Product Information. Plegridy (peginterferon beta-1a)." Biogen Idec Inc, Cambridge, MA.[2] "Product Information. Betaseron (interferon beta-1b)." Berlex, Richmond, CA.[3] "Product Information. Rebif (interferon beta-1a)." Serono Laboratories Inc, Norwell, MA.[4] "Product Information. Avonex (interferon beta-1a)." Biogen, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
