 Medicine. 14th ed." New York, NY: McGraw-Hill Health Professionals Division (1998):[3] CDC. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention/ "Recommendations of the advisory committtee on immunization practices (ACIP): use of vaccines and immune globulins in persons with altered immunocompetence." MMWR Morb Mortal Wkly Rep 42(RR-04) (1993): 1-18', 1767369485);
