henolic acid, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', NULL, 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/13900/', '[1] "Product Information. Campath (alemtuzumab)" Berlex, Richmond, CA.[2] "Product Information. Lonsurf (tipiracil-trifluridine)." Taiho Oncology, Inc., Princeton, NJ.', 1767369485);
